org.docgene.model

Interface ListElement

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ParagraphElement, StyledElement
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    XMLList, XMLListItem

    public interface ListElement
extends ParagraphElement
    Represent any element which can be included in a list. The allowed elements are:
    • "ul" and "ol" lists
    • "li" list elements
